longBusinessSummary: FP Newspapers Inc. publishes, prints, and distributes daily and weekly newspapers, and specialty publications in Manitoba. It owns and publishes the Winnipeg Free Press, Brandon Sun, Canstar Community News division, and the Carillon in Steinbach. The company also delivers advertising materials and provides commercial printing services. FP Newspapers Inc. was founded in 1999 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
